  "text": "For a list of all strains used throughout this work, refer to Introduction of new mutations into E.coli MG1655 were achieved through P1 transduction as previously described [CITATION_1] . Temperature-sensitive FLP recombinase plasmid pCP20 was used for the excision of selective markers as needed [CITATION_2] . All constructs were verified with PCR and sequencing. Primers used throughout this study are listed in Table   1 .2.",
